81ed0ad0-3391-417a-9e1e-e26dc8410a75.do_description: To make the output, you have to...change the colors of all the single-colored structures to the multi-colors. Then change the original multi-colored structure to all black.
81ed0ad0-3391-417a-9e1e-e26dc8410a75.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same.
81ed0ad0-3391-417a-9e1e-e26dc8410a75.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black grid with four different structures. Three are the same color and one is multi-colored.

b550ab6c-fbfc-4cae-846b-22024db85ef5.do_description: To make the output, you have to... REPLACE the solid colored patterns with the multi-colored versions, so each pattern has the same coloring. THEN REMOVE the original multi-colored pattern by replacing it entirely with black tiles.
b550ab6c-fbfc-4cae-846b-22024db85ef5.grid_description: The output grid size... Remains the same as the input grid.
b550ab6c-fbfc-4cae-846b-22024db85ef5.see_description: In the input, you should see... a black grid with patterns placed thought it. One will be multi-colored, and the others will be a solid color.
